BUNG: Large intestine used as a casing.
BURGER: Meat or poultry products labeled with the term "burger" must conform to the standard for hamburger (319.15(b)) and poultry burgers (381.160).
BURGOO: A thick meat or Soup," "Burgoo soup or stew that must contain more than one kind of poultry and vegetables.
