MORTADELLA - POULTRY: Poultry Mortadella is a dry, semi-dry, or cooked sausage formulated with poultry.
The sausage must contain large chunks of pork fat and may contain extenders and/or binders.
Red sweet peppers are permitted up to 4% and pistachio nuts up to 1% and shown as added in the true product name.
